channel.title: About burning music/funny stand up
channel.description:
Yeha this is a useless post since most people here dont give a shit about the law but whatever. I was watching some guy doing stand up(maybe on last comic standing?)and he said "you have all seen those commercials. ya know that say you wouldnt steal a purse, you wouldnt steal a car, so why would u steal music. Well, if my friend said 'i just got a new car, want me to BURN you a copy' I would say hell ya!"
post(or dont).
